sources.title: Chinatown Squad (1935)
sources.description: Lyle Talbot, Valerie Hobson, Andy Devine

metadata.Plot: Chinatown serves as the location where a Communist agent has been killed after he has been caught stealing money. The money was collected from Chinese people living in America. The police chase many leads and suspects until the killer is caught through the efforts of an ex-policeman turned bus driver.
metadata.Writer: Lawrence G. Blochman, Dore Schary, Ben Ryan
metadata.Actors: Lyle Talbot, Valerie Hobson, Hugh O'Connell
